Beyond Domotics devices make your day-to-day life easier by automating your home or office. Connected with Amazon Alexa, your home will be smarter! You can control your equipments by sending voice commands to your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.

Connecting Alexa to your device is simple, you just need to follow a few steps:

1. Download the Beyond Domotics App on Google Play or on the App Store;
2. Access the app and set up an account;
3. Register your devices on the App.It is important that the devices are registered with the same name that will be called when using the skill.
4. Take the opportunity to set up your MOMENTS,which are predefined scenarios according to your preferences. The name of each moment must be the same as the one you will send the command for the skill;
5.In the settings tab, click on "Alexa" to integrate your account on the Amazon platform.
6. Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from your app store;
7. Set up your Alexa device in the application;
8. Look for the skill "Beyond Domotics" in the Skills tab of the Alexa application and enable it;
9. The login screen will open for you to connect;
10. Ready! Now just enjoy your smart home!



Find out what our Skill and equipment can do for you:

Activate moments: create personalized set of actions. For example, you can create the "Wake Up" moment that triggers the alarm clock, turns on the coffee maker, turns on the bedroom lights and starts playing your favorite playlist- "Alexa, turn on Wake up moment".

Turn the lights on and off / dim: are you far from the light switch? You don't have to get off the couch! Just say: "Alexa, turn off the lights in the room". You can also request that Alexa only dim the light if you have dimmable bulbs.

Control equipment: Using our automation equipment, you also control any connected equipment, such as AC’s, television’s, radio’s, coffee makers and etc.
